devdoc.author: Superior Blocks
devdoc.details: Multisig Wallet Smart Contract where multiple “signatures” or approvals  are  needed for an outgoing transfer to take place. As an example, I could create  a multisig wallet with me and my 2 friends. Wallet requires at least 2 to sign any transfer before it is valid. Anyone  can deposit funds into this wallet. But as soon as we want to spend funds,  it requires 2/3 approvals

addOwners(address).details: A method to add an address to the Ownerlist

params._owner: The address to add as a owner.

isOwner(address).details: A method to verify whether an address is a owner on the Ownerlist

returns._0: Whether the address is in the Ownerlist.

removeOwners(address).details: A method to remove a owner from the Ownerlist

params._owner: The address to remove as a owner.
